{"tid":496901,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"睇番謝霆峰得獎呢一幕 真係百感交集","createTime":"2017-12-12T07:28:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-13T05:54:10.000Z","uid":64230,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f1906aa0ada4c661f889a0d283fa7f6d12199826","tid":496901,"uid":64230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T07:28:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7e9G-VuGReI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7e9G-VuGReI&d=yp2e5tveSbr5S2cn2sXZ1wRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=8b16fd4e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7e9G-VuGReI</a><br />\n<br />\n開頭睇到得獎果下<br />\n個死人樣chok到仆街<br />\n已經忍唔住笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但見到張柏芝因為佢而咁感動<br />\n又覺得佢好慘<br />\n帶帽都算 仲要全世界都知<br />\n仲要係自己好朋友派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟住聽佢講得獎感受<br />\n又諗番起其實佢拍戲都幾努力<br />\n英文又好 做生意又叻<br />\n作為男人睇到都覺得佢型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後諗番起佢最近d on9片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又染蝗又剩<br />\n<br />\n只能夠講<br />\n謝霆鋒既一生已經係一部好精彩既電影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c584e57b80f480a3701398789efd76ee6f431f63","tid":496901,"uid":31749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T07:34:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"923cac886207a1c64c6c4bdc7790db4c41bf3ef6","tid":496901,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T07:40:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4b6e980942988bc32a074b4f9095d50499f6949","tid":496901,"uid":64230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T07:42:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我重睇左四次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"h